ImageJ has a lot of keyboard shortcuts.

== Listing all keyboard shortcuts ==

For a verbose list of keyboard shortcuts, call ''Plugins>Shortcuts>List shortcuts...''

== The Command Launcher ==

Use ''Control+L'' (on Mac, ''Command+L'') to open the [[Using the Command Launcher|Command Launcher]], to call menu entries by name.

== Recent Commands ==

To open a list of some recent commands, and a list of the most frequently called commands, hit ''Control+9'' (on Mac, ''Command+9'').

== Open ==

To open new images, type ''Control+O'' (on Mac, ''Command+O'').

